title: Brand Disabled Solo/Duo Q
body:
I can't seem to choose Brand anymore in the champ select (Solo/Duo Q).
Does Anyone Have the same issue?

replies.body: Yeah, I took a look at your account and don't see Brand listed as a champ you own. If you have any questions about how this happened, feel free to reach out in a [**support ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).

Thanks alot buddy, I dont think i owe the champ.
Oh boy do i feel embarrassed now.

Thanks for the quick reply, have a good day

Free rotation champions are not available in ranked. It has to be a champ you own.
I'm not seeing any issues about brand being disabled in the service status page.  Did you get this as a gift?  It might have to do with the account that sent the gift.
